Top10 All-time Players by Positions

Position plays a key role for a player's performance. Top centers normally have more rebounds while top guards tend to give more assists. It is interesting to explore Top10 players by positions to discover best players among their own competitors and find out the huge difference among various positions. In this visualization, players are grouped by their positions and top players of each position are displayed by 5 major measures with 5 tabs to select. A hover tool is also available to show detailed data of players.
